   484‚Üí    ///
   485‚Üí    /// Designates hazardous situations.
   486‚Üí    Warn,
   487‚Üí    /// The "info" level.
   488‚Üí    ///
   489‚Üí    /// Designates useful information.
   490‚Üí    Info,
   491‚Üí    /// The "debug" level.
   492‚Üí    ///
